    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■游戏概要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一边击败蜂拥而来的敌人，一边构建最强构筑，在限制时间内于战场上生存下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家选择的武器与行动将大大改变游戏局势，重复游玩也能乐在其中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■系统</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人，存活到时间结束为止！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243710/extras/bdb347a260a1e0d23b9bbcf56968dc05.avif?t=1751256033\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243710/extras_big/bdb347a260a1e0d23b9bbcf56968dc05.avif?t=1751256033 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合角色专属技能与武器，构建最强构筑，击退蜂拥而来的敌人吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商店解锁武器和强化道具，提升参数，扩展你的战略选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过幸运宝箱一口气强化武器！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243710/extras/143429224f1e5f3023c45ce5db6ccf70.avif?t=1751256033\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243710/extras_big/143429224f1e5f3023c45ce5db6ccf70.avif?t=1751256033 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人后将出现幸运宝箱，开启后启动老虎机，有机会强化武器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目标是大量升级，扭转战局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷你老虎机协助玩家作战！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243710/extras/36452e3095a64e8aa24fd8adf16fced0.avif?t=1751256033\" width=636 height=358 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >画面下方的迷你老虎机若图案一致，将在战场上生成道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >图案何时一致、会获得什么道具，都取决于你在战场上的行动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >锻炼“运气”也许更容易中奖！？</p>",
